# geocode_cache.json is intentionally committed, not ignored: Render's disk
# is ephemeral, so without a seeded cache every cold start re-geocodes all
# ~600+ addresses from scratch at OpenStreetMap's ~1 req/sec rate limit
# (~11 minutes). Shipping a warm cache means cold starts only geocode
# genuinely new addresses. See README.md for how to refresh this file.
